    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fruit Stand Fortune</strong> is an idle game with slot machine and pachinko mechanics. It was designed to be captivating to watch, like a screensaver. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3306030/extras/c2d7e1c0681b293988a622308c5fac98.poster.avif?t=1740551584\" width=800 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3306030/extras/c2d7e1c0681b293988a622308c5fac98.webm?t=1740551584\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3306030/extras/c2d7e1c0681b293988a622308c5fac98.mp4?t=1740551584\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Test your luck</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Slot machines can be clicked for a chance of gaining fruit. Jackpots will triple your winnings! Each slot machine can have up to 3 different fruits types. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3306030/extras/71a1ab5b773d12efb3819d52916df4b2.poster.avif?t=1740551584\" width=420 height=206 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3306030/extras/71a1ab5b773d12efb3819d52916df4b2.webm?t=1740551584\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3306030/extras/71a1ab5b773d12efb3819d52916df4b2.mp4?t=1740551584\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Upgrade your slot machines</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Slot machines can be upgraded to be more efficient! Speed upgrades increase slot spinning speed. Auto-Click makes gathering fruit truly idle, and section upgrades allow you to assign more fruit to a machine, increasing your chances of getting a fruit. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3306030/extras/3fba5fb664f42b181ec138027a51e82c.poster.avif?t=1740551584\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3306030/extras/3fba5fb664f42b181ec138027a51e82c.webm?t=1740551584\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3306030/extras/3fba5fb664f42b181ec138027a51e82c.mp4?t=1740551584\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unlock customers</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customers unlock like achievements, based on your progress! Each customer has a unique unlock condition and behavior. Some customers will increase buying speed, or rain a fruit storm on you! Others will try to steal your money! There are 15+ customers to unlock.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3306030/extras/110223f945c091440a647caf9f27b149.poster.avif?t=1740551584\" width=800 height=406 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3306030/extras/110223f945c091440a647caf9f27b149.webm?t=1740551584\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3306030/extras/110223f945c091440a647caf9f27b149.mp4?t=1740551584\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Will you help Kate the Cat grow her store from a cardboard box to a fruitful business?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3306030/extras/7a02336403409ca5d0b651796a393a5e.poster.avif?t=1740551584\" width=420 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3306030/extras/7a02336403409ca5d0b651796a393a5e.webm?t=1740551584\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3306030/extras/7a02336403409ca5d0b651796a393a5e.mp4?t=1740551584\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
